itemDescription: Commandant of the Royal Air Force Air Cadets

wikipedia_page.main: Air Commodore Dawn Allison McCafferty , is a former officer in both the RAF Reserve and the regular Royal Air Force. She was appointed as Commandant Air Cadets in August 2012, taking over from Barbara Cooper. She retired in July 2020 and was succeeded by Gp Capt John Lawlor as Acting Commandant.
